<section id="hero-section">
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <div class="content-wrapper row middle-xs">
    <h2 class="hero-title col-xs-12">We Are <span>Alluring Labs</span></h2>

    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <div class="temp row between-sm">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12">
          <p>We want to help make your business, or personal brand, succeed. Whether that means making your team and users happy, or helping you devise new solutions to solve your problems; we're here to help!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-7 col-xs-12">
          <p class="contact-us-button-headline">Have Something You'd Like Us To Work On?</p>
          <a tabindex="0" class="contact-us-button" href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="what-we-do">
  <div class="content-wrapper row middle-xs">
    <h3 class="col-xs-12">What We Do</h3>

    <div class="row">
      <article class="thing-we-do col-md-4">
        <div class="thing-wrapper">
          <i class="icon fa fa-code-fork"></i>
          <h4>Development</h4>
          <p>Using the latest and greatest technologies, we can help you improve your existing web applications or make your new idea(s) come to full fruition.</p>
          <p>We also enjoy our sanity, and making the end user happy, so the code we write is concise, clean and easily debuggable.</p>
          <!-- <a href="#github-info">See Our Code</a> -->
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="thing-we-do col-md-4">
        <div class="thing-wrapper">
          <i class="icon fa fa-diamond"></i>
          <h4>UX &amp; UI Design</h4>
          <p>All great systems need to be accompanied by an alluring interface and a near perfect user experience.</p>
          <p>We can bring your idea(s) to life in a visually appealing way; don't make your users deal with a poor experience!</p>
          <!-- <a href="#">See Our Designs</a> -->
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="thing-we-do col-md-4">
        <div class="thing-wrapper">
          <i class="icon fa fa-comments"></i>
          <h4>Consulting</h4>
          <p>Don't know where to start when building your new system?  Perhaps you're stuck in the middle of a project, not knowing where to go?</p>
          <p>Everyone needs a bit of guidance here and there; let our years of experiences guide the path to breathing new life into your old applications, or help pave the way for new ones!</p>
          <!-- <a href="#">Learn More</a> -->
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

