      <p>We love the open source community!  If it's not some super secret, awesome sauce client system, we will generally share it with the community; this even includes the site that you are viewing right now!</p>
      <p>Go ahead, check out what we have made available for the community.</p>

      <div class="github-link">
        <a href="https://github.com/AlluringLabs" target="_blank">github.com/AlluringLabs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
